Global -----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol         Type                  Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| A              Class<A>              -          -             -             |
| B              Class<B>              -          -             -             |
| Bar            Class<Bar>            -          -             -             |
| Baz            Class<Baz>            -          -             -             |
| C              Class<C>              -          -             -             |
| ChildThing     Class<ChildThing>     -          -             -             |
| F              Class<F>              -          -             -             |
| Foo            Class<Foo>            -          -             -             |
| G              Class<G>              -          -             -             |
| Main           Class<Main>           -          -             -             |
| Thing          Class<Thing>          -          -             -             |
| X              Class<X>              -          -             -             |
| Y              Class<Y>              -          -             -             |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: A --------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type               Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| A(int)     Constructor<A>     -          int           -             |
| this       Class<A>           -          -             -             |
| x          int                -          -             -             |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: B extends A ----------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type               Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| B()        Constructor<B>     -          void          -             |
| this       Class<B>           -          -             -             |
| x          int                -          -             A             |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: Bar extends Foo ---------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol      Type                 Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| doStuff     Method               int        void          -             |
| Bar()       Constructor<Bar>     -          void          -             |
| this        Class<Bar>           -          -             -             |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: Baz --------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol           Type                 Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Baz(int,int)     Constructor<Baz>     -          int, int      -             |
| this             Class<Baz>           -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: C extends B ----------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type               Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| C()        Constructor<C>     -          void          -             |
| this       Class<C>           -          -             -             |
| x          int                -          -             A             |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: ChildThing extends Thing ------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol           Type                        Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| ChildThing()     Constructor<ChildThing>     -          void          -             |
| this             Class<ChildThing>           -          -             -             |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: F ----------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol       Type               Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| F(int[])     Constructor<F>     -          int[]         -             |
| this         Class<F>           -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: Foo extends Baz --------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type                 Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Foo()      Constructor<Foo>     -          void          -             |
| this       Class<Foo>           -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: G extends F ----------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type               Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| G(int)     Constructor<G>     -          int           -             |
| this       Class<G>           -          -             -             |
| x          int                -          -             -             |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: Main ---------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type       Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| main       Method     void       String[]      -             |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: Thing ---------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol      Type                   Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Thing()     Constructor<Thing>     -          void          -             |
| this        Class<Thing>           -          -             -             |
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: X -------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol             Type               Return     Signature        Inherited     |
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| X(Thing,Thing)     Constructor<X>     -          Thing, Thing     -             |
| this               Class<X>           -          -                -             |
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Class: Y extends X ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Symbol                               Type               Return     Signature                           Inherited     |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Y(ChildThing,ChildThing)             Constructor<Y>     -          ChildThing, ChildThing              -             |
| Y(ChildThing,ChildThing,boolean)     Constructor<Y>     -          ChildThing, ChildThing, boolean     -             |
| Y(ChildThing,Thing)                  Constructor<Y>     -          ChildThing, Thing                   -             |
| Y(Thing,ChildThing)                  Constructor<Y>     -          Thing, ChildThing                   -             |
| this                                 Class<Y>           -          -                                   -             |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

Constructor: A(int) -----------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type     Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
| x          int      -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

Constructor: B() --------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type     Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
| x          int      -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

