| Symbol     Type     Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
| x          int      -          -             -             |
| y          int      -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

Constructor: C() --------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type     Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
| -          -        -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

Constructor: ChildThing() -----------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type     Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
| -          -        -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

