| Symbol     Type      Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
| arr        int[]     -          -             -             |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+

Constructor: Foo() ------------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type     Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
| -          -        -          -             -             |
+------------------------------------------------------------+

Constructor: G(int) -----------------------------------------+
| Symbol     Type     Return     Signature     Inherited     |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
| x          int      -          -             -             |
